			<div class="post hentry category-uncategorized post_box" id="post-2266">
				<div class="headline_area">
					<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://porkknifeandspoon.com/2011/03/12/bacon-and-strata/" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent link to bacon and strata">bacon and strata</a></h2>
					<p class="headline_meta">by <span class="author vcard fn">Shauna</span> on <abbr class="published" title="2011-03-12">March 12, 2011</abbr></p>
				</div>
				<div class="format_text entry-content">
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-2265" title="strata-and-bacon" src="http://porkknifeandspoon.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/03/strata-and-bacon.jpg" alt="strata-and-bacon" width="426" height="640" /></p>
<p>We went away for the weekend, to do a reading on an island not far from ours, and to have a night&#8217;s getaway.</p>
<p>We chose a little inn at random for a night away. <a href="http://innatvineyardlane.com/">The Inn at Vineyard Lane</a>. We&#8217;re so happy we went there.</p>
<p>Not only were the accommodations spacious and comfy, but the breakfast the next morning? This.</p>
<p>That strata was gluten-free, for me. That bacon was perfectly crisp.</p>
<p>I love weekends away.</p>

<!-- AddThis Button BEGIN -->
<div class="addthis_container"><a href="http://www.addthis.com/bookmark.php" onclick="window.open('http://www.addthis.com/bookmark.php?pub=&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fporkknifeandspoon.com%2F2011%2F03%2F12%2Fbacon-and-strata%2F&amp;title=bacon+and+strata', 'addthis', 'scrollbars=yes,menubar=no,width=620,height=520,resizable=yes,toolbar=no,location=no,status=no'); return false;" title="Bookmark using any bookmark manager!" target="_blank"><img src="http://s7.addthis.com/static/btn/lg-share-en.gif" width="125" height="16" border="0" alt="Bookmark and Share"/></a></div>
